description:
Didier Super (www.didiersuper.com/), Live Bootleg from "Les Nuits Secretes" featuring several otherwise unreleased songs and new material. 

This is a fixed version from previous torrent which had 2 corrupted tracks: 14 and 21; also added tags to files and made a new md5 file for the tagged files.


files are encoded with flac (lossless codec). official site: http://flac.sourceforge.net/

to listen to use flac file under windows I recommend foobar2000 (IMHO the best audio player). official site: http://www.foobar2000.org/

Didier Super is on stage with a whole new show "CONCERT SANS MUSIQUE" everyday but sundays and mondays until new year at Theatre du Temple in Paris 18, rue Fbg du Temple 75011 PARIS

for more info about didier super&#039;s show: www.didiersuper.com/concerts.htm


this flac bootleg and more are available on www.lossless.fr
